rong%3EHow%20Is%20The%20Victim%20Lured%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim%20matches%20with%20the%20woman%20on%20a%20dating%20app%20such%20as%20Tinder%2C%20Bumble%2C%20Hinge%20and%20OKCupid.%20She%20readily%20shares%20her%20WhatsApp%20number%20and%20they%20get%20talking.%20Soon%2C%20a%20date%20is%20planned.%20The%20woman%20then%20insists%20that%20they%20meet%20at%20a%20particular%20locality%20and%20that%20there%20are%20many%20cafes%20and%20pubs%20there.%20When%20the%20victim%20asks%20the%20name%20of%20the%20cafe%20for%20directions%2C%20the%20woman%20tells%20him%20to%20meet%20at%20a%20particular%20Metro%20station%20and%20that%20they%20can%20go%20from%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20cafe%2C%20the%20woman%20places%20the%20order.%20Eager%20to%20impress%20his%20date%2C%20the%20victim%20usually%20does%20not%20suspect%20any%20foul%20play.%20Thereafter%2C%20the%20woman%20orders%20something%20that%20may%20not%20be%20on%20the%20menu.%20In%20some%20case%2C%20the%20woman%20fakes%20an%20emergency%20and%20leaves%20the%20cafe%20in%20a%20hurry.%20When%20the%20bill%20comes%2C%20the%20victim%20realises%20it%20is%20several%20times%20of%20what%20he%20had%20estimated.%20On%20protesting%2C%20he%20is%20threatened%20by%20the%20cafe%20staff%20or%20bouncers.%20Left%20with%20little%20choice%2C%20he%20pays.%20Most%20people%20do%20not%20approach%20the%20police%20because%20a%20probe%20may%20reveal%20to%20his%20family%20that%20he%20is%20meeting%20people%20via%20a%20dating%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMany%20Players%20Involved%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20latest%20Delhi%20incident%20that%20targeted%20an%20IAS%20aspirant%2C%20police%20have%20arrested%20the%20cafe's%20owner%20Akshay%20Pahwa%20and%20the%20victim's%20'date'%20Afsan%20Parveen.%20Police%20said%20this%20scam%20thrives%20on%20an%20elaborate%20mechanism%20involving%20several%20players%20--%20cafe%20owners%2C%20managers%20and%20women%20who%20lure%20the%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20playe