%20as%20Rs%2040%2C000.%20The%20victims%2C%20in%20most%20cases%2C%20do%20not%20file%20a%20police%20complaint%20or%20write%20about%20it%20on%20social%20media%20because%20they%20want%20to%20stay%20anonymous.%20The%20scamsters%20move%20to%20the%20next%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWomen%20Targets%20Too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20men%20who%20are%20becoming%20targets%20on%20dating%20apps.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Delhi%20Police%20arrested%20two%20men%20for%20befriending%20women%20on%20dating%20apps%20and%20allegedly%20robbing%20them%20at%20their%20homes%2C%20PTI%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20identified%20the%20accused%20as%20Vijay%20Kumar%20Kamal%20(28)%20and%20Rahul%20(35).%20The%20matter%20came%20to%20light%20on%20May%2031%20when%20a%2035-year-old%20woman%20filed%20a%20complaint%20that%20a%20man%2C%20who%20introduced%20himself%20as%20Jatin%20on%20a%20dating%20app%2C%20robbed%20her%20in%20her%20house%2C%20senior%20police%20officer%20Ankit%20Singh%20said.%20The%20victim%20told%20the%20police%20that%20she%20and%20Jatin%20(Vijay%20Kumar%20Kamal)%20used%20to%20talk%20over%20messages%20before%20he%20and%20Rahul%20visited%20her%20house%20on%20May%2030.%20They%20tied%20her%20hands%2C%20taped%20her%20mouth%20and%20assaulted%20her%2C%20Singh%20said.%20%26quot%3BBoth%20robbed%20her%20gold%20ornaments%2C%20mobile%20phone%2C%20and%20Rs%205%2C000%20cash%20and%20fled%2C%20the%20officer%20said.%20%26quot%3BWith%20the%20arrest%20of%20the%20accused%2C%20a%20total%20of%20four%20cases%20were%20worked%20out%20of%20Dabri%2C%20Dwarka%20North%2C%20south%20Rohini%2C%20and%20north%20Rohini%20of%20the%20same%20nature.%20Further%20interrogation%20is%20underway%20to%20find%20out%20other%20victims%2C%20if%20any.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719733260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fbebhs8ag_tinder-scam_625x300_30_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-new