ningful.%20Mumbai%20Indians%20(MI)%20supporters%20and%20social%20media%20trolls%20had%20been%20very%20harsh%20to%20Pandya%20during%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMI%20brought%20back%20Pandya%20after%20a%20two-year%20stint%20with%20Gujarat%20Titans%20(GT)%2C%20which%20involved%20winning%20the%20title%20in%20their%20debut%20season%20in%202022%2C%20but%20replacing%20Rohit%20Sharma%20as%20a%20captain%20led%20to%20massive%20social%20media%20backlash%20for%20the%20all-rounder%20and%20franchise.%20Pandya%20was%20booed%20in%20stadiums%20all%20over%20India%20during%20the%20matches%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandya%20said%20that%20India%20were%20calm%20throughout%20the%20game%20and%20always%20believed%20that%20they%20could%20win.%20Despite%20being%20trolled%20mercilessly%20during%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%2C%20on%20a%20personal%20and%20professional%20level%2C%20he%20produced%20what%20may%20have%20been%20the%20World%20Cup-winning%20moment%20when%20he%20removed%20Heinrich%20Klaasen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20means%20a%20lot.%20Very%20emotional%2C%20we'd%20been%20working%20very%20hard%20and%20something%20was%20not%20clicking.%20But%20today%20we%20got%20what%20the%20whole%20nation%20wanted.%20More%20special%20for%20me%2C%20how%20my%20last%206%20months%20were%2C%20I%20haven't%20spoken%20a%20word%2C%20things%20have%20been%20unfair.%20I%20knew%20that%20if%20I%20kept%20working%20hard%20I%20could%20shine%20and%20do%20what%20I%20could%20do.%20Getting%20an%20opportunity%20like%20this%20makes%20it%20more%20special.%20We%20always%20believed%20it%20was%20just%20about%20executing%20our%20plans%20and%20staying%20calm%20and%20letting%20the%20pressure%20come%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Pandya%20said%20in%20a%20post-match%20presentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20in%20grace.%20A%20lot%20was%20said%20by%20people%20who%20don't%20know%20even%20know%20me%20one%20percent%20as%20a%20person.%20People%20have%20spoken%2C%20no%20issues%20but%20I%20have%20always%20believed%20in%20life%20that%20you%20never%20respond%20with%20words%2C%20circumstances%20can%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20time%20for%20fans%20and%20everyone%20else%20to%20learn%20that%20(to%20be%20graceful).%20We%20need%20to%20find%20better%20ways%20to%20conduct%20yourself.%20I%20am%20sure%20the%20same%20people%20will%20be%20happy%2C%26quot%3B%20Hardik%20further%20said%20in%20a%20chat%20with%20the%20broadcaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20be%20honest%2C%20I%20was%20enjoying.%20Very%20few%20get%20these%20life%20changing%20opportunities.%20It%20could%20have%20gone%20the%20other%20way%20as%20well%20today%20but%20I%20see%20it%20glass%20half%20full%20and%20not%20glass%20half%20empty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20not%20taking%20pressure%20and%20focussing%20on%20my%20skill%20sets.%20This%20was%20a%20moment%20written%20in%20the%20stars%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20high%20pressure%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ENothing%20but%20massive%20respect%20for%20you%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhardikpandya7%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40HardikPandya7%3C%2Fa%3E!%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAfter%20his%20recent%20setbacks%2C%20'Kung%20fu%20Pandya'%20narrates%20how%20his%20unwavering%20spirit%2C%20hard%20work%20%26amp%3B%20belief%20led%20to%20his%20comeback%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FT20WorldCup%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23T20WorldCup%3C%2Fa%3E!%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnTune%20in%20to%20watch%20the%20entire%20celebrations%2C%20all%20day%20long%2C%20TODAY%2C%20only%20on%20Star%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FlwxAowAD1A%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FlwxAowAD1A%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Star%20Sports%20(%40StarSportsIndia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%