ng.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20Kevin%20Hochman%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Brinker%20International%2C%20which%20owns%20Chili's%2C%20said%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fseekingalpha.com%2Farticle%2F4687669-brinker-international-inc-eat-q3-2024-earnings-call-transcript%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearnings%20call%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20same-store%20sales%20rose%203.5%25%20in%20the%20third%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHochman%20added%20that%20Chili's%20outperformed%20competitors%20in%20the%20casual%20dining%20industry%20on%20sales%20by%20over%207%25%20and%20on%20traffic%20by%20nearly%204%25%20during%20the%20third%20quarter%2C%20despite%20traffic%20being%20down%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chain%20attributed%20the%20positive%20momentum%20to%20a%20return%20to%20television%20advertising%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20release%20of%20its%20new%20Big%20Smasher%20burger%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-chilis-burger-meal-comparison-review-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edupe%20for%20McDonald's%20Big%20Mac%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20centerpiece%20of%20the%20chain's%20value-focused%20marketing%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurgers%20are%20a%20huge%20area%20of%20opportunity%20for%20casual-dining%20chains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.restaurantbusinessonline.com%2Ffinancing%2Fconsumers-reshape-burger-business%23%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERestaurant%20Business%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20limited-service%20chains%20where%20burgers%20are%20a%20core%20menu%20item%20generated%20%24110%20billion%20in%20total%20sales%20in%202023%2C%20more%20than%20double%20the%20sales%20generated%20by%20limited-service%20chicken%20chains%20like%20Popeyes%20and%20Chick-fil-A.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20data%20was%20limited%20to%20fast-food%20chains%2C%20the%20trend%20extends%20to%20casual-dining%20burger%20chains%20like%20Chili's%20and%20Applebee's.%20Chili's%20is%20also%20attempting%20to