%20%2419.49%2C%20excluding%20tax%2C%20at%20our%20local%20Chili's%20in%20Glendale%2C%20New%20York.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Bacon%20Rancher%20comes%20with%20two%20beef%20patties%2C%20six%20slices%20of%20bacon%2C%20ranch%20dressing%2C%20American%20cheese%2C%20sauteed%20onions%2C%20and%20pickles%20on%20a%20buttered%20brioche%20bun.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chili's%20Bacon%20Rancher%20Burger%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6679d762d1c84a0eaca74fc9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChili's%20Bacon%20Rancher%20Burger.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bacon%20was%20arranged%20in%20a%20criss-cross%20design%20on%20the%20top%20of%20the%20burger%20patties%20and%20cheese.%20There%20were%20two%20slices%20of%20cheese%20on%20the%20burger%20patties%2C%20which%20were%20smashed%20and%20had%20a%20crispy%20texture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThis%20was%20the%20Mount%20Everest%20of%20Chili's%20burgers.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chili's%20Bacon%20Rancher%20Burger%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6679d76250b021b5cae8f363%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChili's%20Bacon%20Rancher%20Burger.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ranch%20dressing%20worked%20well%20with%20the%20other%20ingredients%20in%20the%20burger%20and%20added%20a%20creamy%2C%20tangy%20flavor%20that%20offset%20the%20savoriness%20of%20the%20two%20burger%20patties%20and%20bacon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20we%20thought%20this%20burger%20bordered%20on%20too%20much%20meat.%20We%20couldn't%20clearly%20taste%20the%20bacon%20over%20the%20juicy%2C%20meaty%20flavor%20of%20the%20patties%2C%20and%20the%20moisture%20from%20the%20two%20burgers%20affected%20the%20texture%20of%20the%20bun%2C%20which%20struggled%20to%20hold%20its%20shape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20missed%20some%20of%20the%20fresher%20ingredients%2C%20like%20lettuce%20or%20tomato%2C%20that%20we%20enjoyed%20in%20the%20other%20burgers%20we%20tried.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20this%20burger%20just%20wasn't%20to%20our%20personal%20taste.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20experienced%20similar%20issues%20with%20the%20Double%20Oldtimer%2C%20but%20liked%20the%20toppings%20better.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chili's%20Double%20Oldtimer%20with%20cheese.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6679d76340cf2af6e4f53e66%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChili's%20Double%20Oldtimer%20with%20cheese.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Double%20Oldtimer%20with%20cheese%20cost%20%2417.79%2C%20excluding%20tax%2C%20at%20our%20local%20Chili's%20in%20Glendale%2C%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Double%20Oldtimer%20with%20cheese%20comes%20with%20two%20beef%20patties%2C%20cheddar%20cheese%2C%20pickles%2C%20lettuce%2C%20tomato%2C%20red%20onion%2C%20and%20mustard.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chili's%20Double%20Oldtimer%20with%20cheese.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6679d76250b021b5cae8f366%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChili's%20Double%20Oldtimer%20with%20cheese.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20burgers%20were%20stacked%20neatly%20on%20top%20of%20one%20another%2C%20with%20the%20toppings%20under%20the%20beef.%20We%20thought%20this%20was%20interesting%20%E2%80%94%20we%20usually%20place%20burger%20toppings%20on%20top%20of%20the%20patties%20to%20prevent%20the%20bottom%20bun%20from%20getting%20soggy.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThis%20burger%20tasted%20strongly%20of%20mustard%2C%20but%20we%20enjoyed%20the%20classic%20toppings.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chili's%20Double%20Oldtimer%20w%2FCheese%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6679d76150b021b5cae8f362%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChili's%20Double%20Oldtimer%20with%20cheese.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20thin%20slice%20of%20cheese%20separated%20the%20two%20burger%20patties%2C%20and%20we%20thought%20the%20lettuce%20and%20tomato%20tasted%20fresh.%20However%2C%20we%20had%20mixed%20feelings%20about%20the%20mustard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mustard%20almost%20overpowered%20the%20other%20ingredients%2C%20and%20the%20additional%20patty%20made%20the%20burger%20so%20juicy%20that%20the%20bread%20was%20nearly%20flattened.%20Still%2C%20we%20thought%20the%20burger%20patties%20were%20cooked%20perfectly%20and%20had%20an%20excellent%20texture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20great%20classic%20burger%2C%20similar%20to%20one%20we%20might%20make%20at%20a%20cookout.%20However%2C%20we%20all%20agreed%20that%20when%20dining%20out%2C%20we%20prefer%20to%20choose%20more%20creative%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20also%20tried%20the%20single-patty%20Oldtimer%20burger%20without%20cheese.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chili's%20Oldtimer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6679d762d1c84a0eaca74fc7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChili's%20Oldtimer.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Oldtimer%20cost%20%2413.29%2C%20excluding%20tax%2C%20at%20our%20local%20Chili's%20in%20Glendale%2C%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Oldtimer%20comes%20with%20one%20burger%20patty%2C%20lettuce%2C%20tomato%2C%20red%20onion%2C%20and