nitely%20going%20to%20need%20significantly%20better%20battery%20performance%20and%20it's%20our%20belief%20that%20the%20way%20that%20we%20get%20there%20is%20by%20doing%20battery%20development%20in%20a%20fundamentally%20different%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f50cf130-8c6d-4c06-88f7-4cd95c5ec07b%5C%22%3EBoosting%20batteries%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDesigning%20EV%20batteries%20is%20a%20three-step%20process%2C%20Georgia%20Tech%20assistant%20professor%20Micah%20Ziegler%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScientists%20must%20first%20decide%20on%20a%20structure%20and%20combination%20of%20elements%20that%20will%20produce%20a%20battery%20material%20with%20the%20desired%20properties%20before%20developing%20a%20recipe%20to%20synthesize%20it%20and%20testing%20that%20material%20in%20a%20lab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sheer%20number%20of%20potential%20combinations%20and%20the%20variety%20of%20demands%20placed%20on%20EV%20batteries%20%E2%80%94%20including%20longevity%2C%20safety%2C%20cost%2C%20and%20charging%20speed%20%E2%80%94%20makes%20designing%20batteries%20a%20lengthy%20and%20difficult%20process%2C%20Ziegler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20number%20of%20options%20is%20just%20vast.%20Once%20you%20start%20putting%20different%20elements%20together%2C%20we're%20talking%20about%20potentially%20trillions%20of%20different%20combinations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20could%20dramatically%20speed%20up%20this%20process%2C%20identifying%20potentially%20promising%20combinations%20far%20quicker%20than%20humans%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKarl%20Mueller%2C%20a%20physical%20chemist%20at%20the%20Pacific%20Northwest%20National%20Laboratory%2C%20described%20battery%20design%20as%20an%20%26quot%3BEdisonian%26quot%3B%20task%3A%20a%20drawn-out%20process%20of%20trial%20and%20error%20in%20which%20scientists%20compare%20and%20tweak%20billions%20of%20chemical%20combinations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20process%20is%20slow%2C%20and%20it%20can%20take%20years%20to%20find%20new%20materials%20and%20modify%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPNNL%20recently%20teamed%20up%20with%20Microsoft%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-discovers-new-material-to-reduce-lithium-use-in-batteries-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ediscover%20a%20promising%20new%20material%20for%20making%20EV%20batteries%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20the%20latter's%20AI%20and%20cloud-computing%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20solid-state%20electrolyte%20they%20discovered%20relies%20less%20on%20lithium%2C%20an%20increasingly%20rare%20resource%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flithium-mining-electric-vehicles-climate-crisis-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eforms%20the%20core%20of%20today's%20EV%20batteries%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20is%20also%20less%20likely%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-vehicle-fires-what-to-know-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecatch%20fire%20than%20lithium-ion%20batteries%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a46cbe36-086b-4aac-8168-fdc9fda00339%5C%22%3E'It's%20going%20to%20be%20phenomenal'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMueller%20said%20incorporating%20AI%20into%20PNNL's%20workflow%20allowed%20the%20lab%20to%20dramatically%20speed%20up%20the%20process%20of%20whittling%20down%2032%20million%20possible%20chemical%20combinations%20to%20around%2020%20potential%20battery%20designs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20newest%20AI%20tools%20that%20we've%20been%20working%20on%20with%20Microsoft%2C%20it's%20allowed%20us%20to%20design%20for%20specific%20properties%20and%20to%20weed%20out%20things%20early%20that%20we%20believe%20won't%20have%20those%20properties%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20be%20phenomenal%20for%20speeding%20up%20the%20discovery%20process.%20I%20think%20it's%20going%20to%20drive%20the%20speed%20of%20the%20discovery%20for%20what%20we%20need%20to%20do%20to%20allow%20for%20more%20electrification%20and%20better%20electric%20vehicles%2C%26quot%3B%20Mueller%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hype%20around%20generative%20AI%20may%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-earnings-mark-zuckerberg-ai-spending-tech-investors-stock-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efading%20in%20some%20quarters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20one%20area%20where%20it's%20already%20reaping%20clear%20benefits%20is%20the%20scientific%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EModels%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F77bf38b7-114d-44c8-956e-1e39e39ecb52%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeepMind's%20AlphaFold%203%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20improved%20the%20mapping%20of%20complex%20biological%20proteins%2C%20potentially%20opening%20up%20new%20opportunities%20for%20researchers%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeepmind-alphafold-ai-origin-story-impact-on-biotech-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equickly%20develop%20life-saving%20drugs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMueller%20said%20that%20PNNL's%20collaboration%20with%20Microsoft%20has%20convinced%20him%20that%20generative%20AI%20could%20have%20applications%20far%20beyond%20speeding%20up%20EV%20battery%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20idea%20of%20building%20science%20agents%20based%20around%20large%20language%20models%20and%20coupling%20that%20to%20these%20discovery%20workflows%2C%20is%20very%2C%20very%20exciting%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20in%20a%20year%20or%20two%20we're%20not%20going%20to%20recognize%20where%20science%20has%20got%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fev-batteries-ai-cars-transport-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719666542000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667d4f3d50b0