.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-11-1719572578-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-11-1719572578-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FInfographic-website-11-1719572578-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354835%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Smarika%20Chandrakar%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719579178000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika1-1719549336.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D354716%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Smarika%20Chandrakar%20quit%20a%20thriving%20corporate%20career%20to%20become%20a%20full-time%20farmer%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%20With%20125%20people%20employed%20in%20her%20fields%2C%20she%20hopes%20to%20introduce%20advanced%20technology%20to%20improve%20productivity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354716%2Fvegetable-farmer-smarika-chandrakar-grows-tomatoes-cucumbers-brinjals-in-chhattisgarh-farming-mba-grad-earns-crores%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Homemaker%20to%20Entrepreneur%3A%20Woman%20Found%20Financial%20Freedom%20in%20Coconut%20Biz%2C%20Earns%20Rs%2020%20Lakh%2FMonth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNever%20in%20my%20wildest%20dream%20did%20I%20ever%20think%20of%20becoming%20an%20entrepreneur.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20experience%20in%20the%20business%20field%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sumila%20Jayaraj%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Greenaura%2C%20a%20company%20which%20sells%20coconut-based%20products%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20the%20small%20town%20of%20Engandiyur%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Sumila%E2%80%99s