0768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSumila-2-1719576057-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354857%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESumila%20believes%20launching%20her%20own%20company%20was%20a%20turning%20point%20for%20her.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20part%20of%20my%20job%2C%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20testimonials.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20came%20to%20know%20about%20a%20doctor%20who%20was%20using%20virgin%20coconut%20oil%20to%20treat%20ulcers%20in%20children%20who%20were%20cancer%20patients.%20Usually%2C%20children%20develop%20painful%20ulcers%20in%20their%20mouth%20post%20chemotherapy.%20This%20testimonial%20really%20surprised%20me%20and%20also%20ignited%20the%20passion%20inside%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20three%20years%20into%20her%20first%20job%2C%20Sumila%20quit%20the%20job%20to%20start%20her%20own%20company%20from%20a%20small%20shed%20adjacent%20to%20her%20house.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20mission%20was%20to%20develop%20as%20many%20value-added%20products%20from%20coconuts%20and%20advertise%20their%20goodness%20to%20the%20whole%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20explains%20how%20she%20uses%20the%20centrifugal%20method%20to%20make%20cold-pressed%20virgin%20coconut%20oil%20instead%20of%20the%20hot-pressed%20oil%20method.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20getting%20the%20coconuts%2C%20we%20separate%20the%20oil%20from%20coconut%20milk%20using%20the%20centrifugal%20machine.%20Traditionally%2C%20the%20oil%20is%20produced%20by%20heating%20the%20coconut%20milk%20and%20is%20processed%20after%20boiling%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%2C%20in%20the%20centrifugal%20method%2C%20the%20coconuts%20are%20pressed%20gently%20and%20milk%20is%20spun%20at%2010%2C000%20revolutions%20per%20minute%20in%20the%20machine.%20Without%20any%20heating%20process%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20retain%20more%20nutrients%20and%20antioxidants%20in%20this%20method%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20virgin%20coconut%20oil%2C%20Sumila%20is%20manufacturing%2013%20other%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328024%2Fengineer-turns-farmer-startup-tengin-makes-products-of-coconuts-earns-lakhs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoconut-based%20products%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSumila-3-1719576105.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202021%2C%20Sumila%20launched%20her%20company%20%E2%80%98Greenaura%E2%80%99%20that%20sells%20products%20like%20virgin%20coconut%20oil%2C%20milk%20powder%2C%20and%20vinegar.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSumila-3-1719576105.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSumila-3-1719576105-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSumila-3-1719576105-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSumila-3-1719576105-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FSumila-3-1719576105-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354859%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%202021%2C%20Sumila%20launched%20her%20company%20%E2%80%98Greenaura%E2%80%99%20that%20sells%20products%20like%20virgin%20coconut%20oil%2C%20milk%20powder%2C%20and%20vinegar.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20challenges%20in%20establishing%20the%20company%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20have%20any%20business