EHere%20are%20the%20tips%20she%20shared%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon%E2%80%99t%20fret%20over%20writing%20the%20%E2%80%98perfect%20answer%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20struggled%20with%20answer%20writing%20initially%2C%20her%20friend%20advised%20her%20to%20add%20data%20and%20reports%20and%20focus%20on%20bringing%20originality%20to%20the%20answer%20rather%20than%20a%20%E2%80%98copy-pasted%E2%80%99%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFind%20a%20peer%20group%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20review%20her%20answers%2C%20she%20joined%20a%20Mains%20answer%20writing%20peer%20group%20to%20share%20and%20learn.%20She%20shared%20that%20they%20would%20write%20two%20answers%20daily%20and%20review%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%223%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EPractice%2C%20practice%2C%20practice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20looked%20at%20answers%20of%20toppers%20to%20help%20in%20better%20comprehension.%20%E2%80%9CAnything%20without%20practice%20seems%20tough%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%224%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFocus%20on%20the%20optional%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETry%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353815%2Fias-officer-ashish-kumar-singhal-jaipur-cleared-upsc-cse-after-four-failures-topper%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomplete%20your%20optional%20subject%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20November%2C%20she%20says.%20For%20this%2C%20you%20should%20dedicate%20at%20least%20six%20hours%20every%20day%20to%20the%20optional%20with%20remaining%20time%20for%20general%20studies.%20She%20would%20start%20her%20day%20with%20the%20optional%20from%208%20AM%20to%2012%20PM%20and%20from%201%20to%203%20PM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%225%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C