edy%20he%20had%20witnessed%20on%20a%20ferry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20part%20of%20my%20work%2C%20I%20kept%20travelling%20to%20rural%20remote%20corners%20and%20observed%20that%20there%20was%20no%20sustained%20healthcare%20system%20in%20these%20islands.%20I%20also%20came%20across%20a%20case%20of%20a%20young%20woman%20who%20died%20during%20childbirth%20on%20the%20ferry.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20the%20whole%20thing%20hit%20me%20pretty%20hard%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-4-1719399670.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22These%20boat%20clinics%20are%20equipped%20with%20vaccines%20for%20newborn%20babies%20to%20protect%20them%20from%20measles%2C%20Japanese%20encephalitis%2C%20polio%2C%20etc.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-4-1719399670.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-4-1719399670-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-4-1719399670-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-4-1719399670-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-4-1719399670-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354368%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThese%20boat%20clinics%20are%20equipped%20with%20vaccines%20for%20newborn%20babies%20to%20protect%20them%20from%20measles%2C%20Japanese%20encephalitis%2C%20polio%2C%20etc.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAssam%E2%80%99s%20maternal%20mortality%20ratio%20was%20also%20the%20highest%20in%20the%20country%20back%20then%20in%20the%20late%201990s%20and%20continues%20to%20be%20so%20even%20today%20despite%20the%20slight%20improvement%20%5B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcensusindia.gov.in%2Fnada%2Findex.php%2Fcatalog%2F44379%2Fdownload%2F48052%2FSRS_MMR_Bulletin_2018_2020.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E195%20per%20100%2C000%20live%20births%3C%2Fa%3E%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Assam%2C%20there%20are%202%2C500%20islands%20and%20most%20of%20them%20are%20inhabited.%20I%20wanted%20to%20work%20on%20an%20idea%20that%20involved%20the%20support%20of%20local%20people%20and%20the%20state%20government%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20these%20people%20and%20improve%20the%20health%20conditions%20of%20the%20poor%20and%20the%20vulnerable%20communities%2C%20especially%20the%20women%20and%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20can%E2%80%99t%20build%20roads%20everywhere%20and%20certainly%20can%E2%80%99t%20have%20helicopters%20give%20services%20throughout%20the%20year.%20So%2C%20we%20shifted%20to%20the%20traditional%20system%20of%20using%20boats%20and%20to%20look%20upon%20the%20river%20as%20an%20ally%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sanjoy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20collaboration%20with%20the%20National%20Rural%20Health%20Mission%2C%20the%20non-profit%20launched%20the%20boat%20clinics%20in%202005%20to%20bridge%20the%20healthcare%20divide.%20Since%20then%2C%20monthly%20health%20camps%20have%20been%20organised%20across%2014%20districts%20including%20Dibrugarh%2C%20Tinsukia%2C%20Jorhat%2FMajuli%2C%20Sonitpur%2C%20and%20Nalbari.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20purpose%2C%2015%20such%20floating%20health%20clinics%20are%20operating%20along%20the%20river%20to%20cater%20to%20the%20isolated%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20month%2C%20a%20team%20comprising%20two%20medical%20officers%2C%20laboratory%20technician%2C%20pharmacist%2C%20and%20three%20nurses%20reach%20out%20to%20offer%20primary%20healthcare%20at%20the%20island%20itself.%20These%20boat%20clinics%20are%20equipped%20with%20vaccines%20for%20newborn%20babies%20to%20protect%20them%20from%20measles%2C%20Japanese%20encephalitis%2C%20polio%2C%20etc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20conducts%20routine%20immunisations%20for%20pregnant%20women%20and%20also%20has%20a%20provision%20to%20test%20haemoglobin%2C%20blood%20glucose%20levels%2C%20sickle%20cell%20anaemia%2C%20and%20tuberculosis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-3-1719399627.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20team's%20focus%20is%20on%20routine%20immunisation%2C%20primary%20healthcare%20services%2C%20child%20and%20antenatal%20care.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-3-1719399627.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-3-1719399627-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-3-1719399627-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-3-1719399627-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-3-1719399627-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354367%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20team%E2%80%99s%20focus%20is%20on%20routine%20immunisation%2C%20primary%20healthcare%20services%2C%20child%20and%20antenatal%20care.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESolar%20energy%20to%20the%20rescue%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighlighting%20the%20challenges%20in%20running%20the%20programme%2C%20Riturekha%20Barua%2C%20the%20district%20programme%20officer%20of%20Majuli%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CUsually%2C%20we%20have%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20boats%20for%2018%20days%20in%20a%20month.%20The%20boat%20was%20our%20home.%20So%2C%20while%20patients%20go%20back%20to%20their%20homes%2C%20we%20could%20not.%20We%20slept%20in%20our%20respective%20beddings%20here%2C%20far%20away%20from%20the%20comforts%20of%20our%20homes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20used%20kerosene-based%20generators%20for%20power%20but%20it%20would%20only%20help%20for%203%20to%204%20hours%20in%20a%20day.%20It%20would%20become%20challenging%20and%20uneasy%20for%20us%20to%20live%20on%20the%20boat%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20summer%20heat.%20Secondly%2C%20we%20did%20not%20have%20any%20cold%20storage%20facility%20for%20vaccines.%20Having%20a%20permanent%20energy%20supply%20was%20crucial%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20the%20non-profit%20decided%20to%20harness%20solar%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20C-NES%20partnered%20with%20the%20Bengaluru-based%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F114009%2Fboat-clinics-brahmaputra-healthcare-boat-clinics-switching-solar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESELCO%20Foundation%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20works%20to%20bring%20sustainable%20energy%20solutions%20to%20rural%20and%20urban%20communities%20in%20the%20country.%20As%20part%20of%20this%2C%20the%20large%20boats%20were%20equipped%20with%20solar%20panels%20of%203%20KV%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20solar%20power%20can%E2%80%99t%20drive%20vessels%20on%20a%20river%20as%20powerful%20as%20the%20Brahmaputra.%20So%2C%20we%20use%20it%20to%20run%20lighting%20and%20basic%20services%20like%20fans.%20Apart%20from%20this%2C%20the%20cold%20chains%20for%20chilling%20units%20which%20store%20and%20carry%20vaccines%20and%20other%20life-sa