eel%20the%20capacity%20of%20the%20solar%20panels%20should%20be%20increased%20for%20better%20results.%20Last%20night%2C%20the%20solar-powered%20fans%20could%20only%20last%20till%209%3A30.%20We%20had%20to%20turn%20on%20the%20generator%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20night.%20If%20the%20capacity%20is%20increased%2C%20we%20will%20be%20able%20to%20retire%20to%20bed%20and%20sleep%20peacefully%20after%20a%20hectic%20day%20providing%20quality%20service%20to%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20healthcare%20provider%20believes%20the%20capacity%20must%20be%20increased%2C%20Riturekha%20says%20that%20with%20the%20additional%20support%20of%20solar%20energy%2C%20the%20floating%20health%20clinic%20is%20successfully%20catering%20to%20about%2010%2C000%20patients%20in%20the%20district%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20soil%20erosion%20and%20regular%20flooding%20in%20the%20region%2C%20it%20has%20been%20a%20challenge%20to%20build%20a%20permanent%20structure%20in%20these%20places%20which%20leads%20to%20medical%20apathy%20for%20the%20residents.%20But%20with%20these%20boat%20clinics%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20bridge%20the%20healthcare%20divide%20in%20remote%20areas%20of%20the%20islands%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Riturekha%20Barua%20and%20Dr%20Saddam%20Hussain.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719404622000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fassam-2-1719399558.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D354362%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20reporting%20from%20rural%20parts%20of%20Assam%2C%20Sanjoy%20Hazarika%20noticed%20the%20intense%20need%20for%20a%20sustained%20healthcare%20system%20in%20the%20region.%20In%20collaboration%20with%20the%20National%20Rural%20Health%20Mission%2C%20his%20non-profit%2C%20C-NES%2C%20launched%20boat%20clinics%20in%202005%20to%20bridge%20the%20he