cines%2Fhcp%2Fconversations%2Funderstanding-vacc-work.html%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Photo%20credit%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.myvaccinationhub.in%5C%22%3Ehttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.myvaccinationhub.in%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719311809000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIn-betweeen-article-image_GSK-1-1719303286.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D354182%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20you%E2%80%99re%20above%2050%20and%20have%20had%20chickenpox%20before%2C%20there%20is%20a%20risk%20of%20developing%20shingles%20%E2%80%94%20a%20viral%20infection%20caused%20by%20the%20varicella-zoster%20virus%20(VZV).%20The%20best%20way%20to%20prevent%20it%20is%20with%20the%20vaccination.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20all%20about%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TBI%20Team%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354182%2Fshingles-symptoms-treatment-vaccination-chickenpox-virus-glaxosmithkline-pharmaceutical-vaccine%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98I%20Feel%20Like%20a%20King%E2%80%99%3A%20Farmer%20Earns%20Rs%2015%20Lakh%2FAcre%20by%20Making%20a%20Switch%20From%20Rubber%20Cultivation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKerala%20is%20the%20largest%20rubber%20producer%20in%20the%20country.%20More%20than%20a%20decade%20back%2C%20its%20rubber%20production%20started%20falling%20as%20growers%20found%20it%20unprofitable%20owing%20to%20rising%20production%20costs%20and%20falling%20prices%20amid%20cheap%20imports%20from%20Vietnam%20and%20Indonesia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBordering%20Karnataka%2C%20Ulikkal%20village%20in%20the%20Kannur%20district%20was%20a%20lush%20landscape%20that%20was%20once%20predominantly%20a%20rubber-growing%20area.%20Among%20millions%20of%20rubber%20farmers%2C%20Biju%20Narayanan%E2%80%99s%20family%20who%20cultivated%20rubber%20on%20one-third%20of%20the%20farmland%2C%20also%20lost%20their%20major%20income%20source%20with%20plummeting%20profitability.%20It%20became%20costlier%20to%20produce%20rubber%20than%20to%20sell%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20cost%20of%20production%20was%20around%20Rs%20160%20per%20kg%20and%20the%20selling%20price%20was%20Rs%20110%20per%20kg.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20rates%20in%20rubber%20were%20dwindling%20as%20farmers%20could%20fetch%20only%20Rs%20100%20per%20kg%20from%20rubber.%20A%20labourer%20could%20earn%20more%20wages%20daily.%20It%20was%20not%20sufficient%20for%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiju%20reconsidered%20the%20agricultural%20practices%20and%20made%20the%20bold%20decision%20to%20replace%20seven%20acres%20of%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20rubber%20trees%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F295835%2Fcoconut-farmer-senior-citizen-grows-mangosteen-from-malaysia-exports-to-gulf-countries%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexotic%20fruits%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20rambutan%2C%20mangosteen%2C%20pepper%2C%20areca%20nut%2C%20coconut%2C%20cashew%2C%20and%20other%20crops.%20%E2%80%9CI%20axed%20most%20of%20the%20rubber%20trees%20to%20try%20new%20plantations.%20People%20called%20me%20a%20madman%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20the%20progressive%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-1_11zon-1719236290.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Biju%20opted%20for%20high-density%20plantations%20and%20multi-crops%20to%20maximise%20returns%20from%20land.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-1_11zon-1719236290.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-1_11zon-1719236290-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-1_11zon-1719236290-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-1_11zon-1719236290-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FBiju-1_11zon-1719236290-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354131%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBiju%20opted%20for%20high-density%20plantations%20and%20multi-crops%20to%20maximise%20returns%20from%20land.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20decision%2C%20once%20criticised%20and%20deemed%20as%20madness%20by%20many%2C%20including%20his%20own%20family%2C%20has%20since%20blossomed%20into%20a%20lucrative%20agribusiness%20model.%20%E2%80%9CI%20knew%20I%20must%20prove%20my%20decision%20correct%20because%20my%20family%2C%20neighbours%2C%20and%20friends%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20crazy%20decision.%20I%20took%20it%20as%20a%20challenge%20and%20turned%20agriculture%20into%20agri-business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Biju%20earns%20Rs%209%20to%2015%20lakh%20per%20acre%20from%20rambutan%20farming%20alone.%20We%20sat%20down%20with%20him%20to%20understand%20how%20he%20rewrote%20the%20traditional%20farming%20script.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaximising%20yield%20with%20multi-crops%20on%20the%20same%20land%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiju%20is%20a%20mechanical%20engineer%20by%20profession.%20Educated%20at%20Dakshina%20Kannada%E2%80%99s%20KVG%20College%20of%20Engineering%2C%20he%20initially%20juggled%20his%20studies%20with%20managing%20the%20family%20farm.%20At%2018%2C%20when%20he%20was%20in%20his%20first%20year%20of%20college%2C%20he%20lost%20his%20father%20and%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20farm%20fell%20on%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3